### Admin Achievements API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@adminToken = WRONG_VALUE
@email = user@example.com
@key = public-sponsor

### -----------------------------------------------------------------------
### Allowed keys for @key (granted achievements only):
###   public-sponsor   → Project Patron
###   contributor      → Contributor
###   bug-hunter       → Bug Hunter
###   playstore-beta   → Play Store Pioneer
### -----------------------------------------------------------------------


### List achievements granted to a user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/achievements?email={{email}}
x-admin-token: {{adminToken}}


### Grant an achievement to a user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/achievements
x-admin-token: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "key": "{{key}}"
}


### Remove an achievement from a user
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/achievements?email={{email}}&key={{key}}
x-admin-token: {{adminToken}}


### --- Quick presets -------------------------------------------------------

### Grant: Project Patron
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/admin/achievements
x-admin-token: {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "key": "public-sponsor"
}


